Subject: [eVuln] "my little homepage" products [link] BBCode XSS Vulnerability


New eVuln Advisory:
"my little homepage" products [link] BBCode XSS Vulnerability
http://evuln.com/vulns/51/summary.html

--------------------Summary----------------
Vendor: my little homepage
Vendor's Web Site: http://www.mylittlehomepage.net/
Software: All products
Versions: 2004.04.20
Critical Level: Harmless
Type: Cross-Site Scripting
Class: Remote
Status: Unpatched
Exploit: Available
Solution: Not Available
Discovered by: Aliaksandr Hartsuyeu (eVuln.com)
eVuln ID: EV0051

-----------------Description---------------
Arbitrary script code insertion is possible in BBcode [link] tag of all "my little homepage" products:

my little weblog - checked
my little guestbook - checked
my little forum - checked

Other products may be vulnerable too.

[link] tag isn't properly sanitized. This can be used to post arbitrary script code.

--------------Exploit----------------------
Available at: http://evuln.com/vulns/51/exploit.html


--------------Solution---------------------
No Patch available.

--------------Credit-----------------------
Discovered by: Aliaksandr Hartsuyeu (eVuln.com)


